item.title: migrate

item.title: status
item.description: cdsctl admin cdn status display the status of cdn Synopsis display the status of cdn cdsctl admin cdn status [flags] Examples cdsctl admin cdn status Options --fields string Only display specified object fields. 'empty' will display all fields, 'all' will display all object fields, 'field1,field2' to select multiple fields --filter string Filter output based on conditions provided --format string Output format: table|json|yaml (default "table") -q, --quiet Only display object's key --verbose Display all object fields Options inherited from parent commands -c, --context string cdsctl context name -f, --file string set configuration file --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers.
